  "source_id": "liver-cancer-staging",
  "name": "Liver Cancer Staging - Comprehensive Workup Query (HCC + Labs + Imaging)",
  "description": "Tests ability to find HCC patients with full staging workup. Per PheKB algorithm, the cohort requires HCC dx + CT abdomen + 4 staging labs (AFP, Albumin, Bilirubin, INR).",
  "prompt": "Find HCC patients who underwent comprehensive staging workup including CT abdomen and AFP, albumin, bilirubin, and INR labs.",
  "prompts": {
    "naive": "Find HCC staging patients.",
    "broad": "Find hepatocellular carcinoma (HCC) patients with comprehensive staging workup — CT abdomen imaging plus AFP, albumin, bilirubin, and INR labs (per AJCC/BCLC/CLIP staging systems).",
    "expert": "Run multiple queries. (1) Condition?code=http://snomed.info/sct|25370001 — HCC. (2) Procedure?code=http://snomed.info/sct|169070004 — CT abdomen. (3) Observation?code=http://loinc.org|1834-1 — AFP. Union the patient IDs."
  },
